title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Antarleen
subTitle: Aniket Sanyal, a detective, is forced to resume work during his much-needed, long vacation after a mysterious death of a tourist.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Shiva reveals his divine form in front of everyone in the palace. Mainadevi seeks Lord Shiva's help to solve her problem.

title: Baishe Srabon
subTitle: A serial killer terrorises the city, murdering innocent victims and leaving verses of Bengali poetry beside their bodies. The police enlist the help of a retired officer to track down the killer.

title: Amar Bodyguard
subTitle: After confessing his love, Anol comes to know that he is like a bodyguard to Ankhi. Later, she realises his feelings and sorts out their problems.

title: Idiot
subTitle: Samrat's relationship with Anjali is threatened when her cruel brother disapproves of him. In order to win him over, Samrat pretends to be a successful businessman.

title: Bhalobasa Bhalobasa
subTitle: Sidhu meets and falls in love with a woman named Priya despite being engaged to a different girl. He soon has to make a choice between following his heart and respecting his father's wishes.

title: Le Chakka
subTitle: Abir relocates with his family to Dorjipara, which is home to 11 bullets, a cricket team that is out of luck. He also discovers that the locality is being threatened by a political goon.

title: Fighter, Marbo Noy Morbo
subTitle: Surya, a college student, decides to exact revenge on a local gangster after he frames and kills his elder brother, ACP Bose.

title: Bibaho Obhijaan
subTitle: While Rajat's wife is extremely religious, Anupam's wife is a busy activist. Soon, Rajat and Anupam face hilarious situations in their marriage as they are frustrated with their wives.

title: Bibaho Obhijaan

title: Autograph
subTitle: Samar, a deep-sea diver, revisits the memories of his past relationships. He cherishes the moments of joy and appreciates the contribution of all the people who are a part of his life.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainadevi requests Lord Shiva to choose between the curse and his love for Parvati. Tarakasura conspires against Mainadevi.

title: Sabar Upare Maa
subTitle: Sumi is separated from her parents when she is a child. Years later, when Sumi gets framed for a murder she did not commit, her mother, who is a lawyer, comes to her rescue.

title: Refugee
subTitle: Estranged from his family, Shiva grows up to become a refugee and helps the needy. One day, he comes across his family only to learn that his jealous brother doesn't want him back.

title: Bidhilipi
subTitle: A schoolmaster's former student, Bablu, falls in love with his daughter, Minu. However, Minu is in love with another man, Alok, and wants to marry him.

title: Satrur Muqubila
subTitle: Awbhoy, a dedicated police officer, develops a deep romantic interest in a young woman attending a job interview while undergoing training.

title: Sangee
subTitle: When Bijay comes to Calcutta for higher studies, he meets Rupa and instantly falls in love with her. However, he is unaware that she is his friend Rana's sister.

title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Swabhumi
subTitle: A woman begins looking for her husband amidst a civil war that breaks out over land acquisition in her village.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati feels joyful when Lord Shiva gets disguised as a woman to meet her. Mainadevi tries to convince Parvati not to marry Lord Shiva.

title: Gogoler Kirti
subTitle: A young detective visits his ancestral village during his summer vacation. However, the vacation quickly turns into an exhilarating adventure after an invaluable family heirloom goes missing.

title: Agni Pariksha
subTitle: Raja Babu is in love with a beautiful young woman and wishes to marry her. However, his life changes after she suddenly passes away in an accident.

title: Amanush
subTitle: Vinod, an orphan, finds his soul mate in Rhea, who cares a lot for him but loves Aditya. Dejected and irate, Vinod becomes a psychopath killer to win her over.

title: Greftaar
subTitle: Arun Roy, a police sub-inspector, comes face-to-face with a corrupt political leader, Indrajit, and stands up to him. As a result, his father is humiliated and suspended from the police.

title: Barood
subTitle: Shaon, a loafer, and Jui, an innocent girl are in love with each other. They want to live the life of their dreams together but circumstances turn their lives upside down.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Wanted
subTitle: The police kill Shibu, an innocent man, after mistaking him to be his lookalike Raja, an assassin. To escape from the police, Raja starts living with Shibu's parents as their son.
